#### 0.2.0
## Bug
   + note_off not working
   - Low shelf is an anti-noise gate
   - Block rendering when reversing.

## Filters class.
   - simple and fast lp.
   - 2-pole LP, HP, BP
   - LP24
   - BP24
   - HP24
   - ?notch
   - SVF

## Sample class
   * basic sampler
   - velocity support
   + normalize
   + reverse
   * fine pitch
     * Pitch envelop.
   + Antialias filter?
   + Filter support
     + Filter Envelop.
   - Envelops
     * EnvSwitcher, EnvDecay, EnvHold
     + End Dahdsr

## Promethee

## Promethee GUI
   * GUI Base.
   * Envelopview
     * filter{cut | res}
     * amp
     * pan
     * pitch
   - WaveView
     - Shared memory.
   * gain, pitch, pan, root
   - filter view and/or filter sliders
   * antialias, reverse, normalize button.

